Bone key is used in the Shilo Village quest to open and enter Rashiliyia's Tomb. It can be made by using a chisel on a bone shard. Besides this function, it has no further use besides selling it to Yanni Salika for 100 gp.

The bone key can be added to the steel key ring to save bank space. Attempting to drop it will result in the chatbox stating This looks quite valuable. As you go to throw the item away Zadimus' words come to you again. 'I am the key, but only kin may approach her'.

If lost, it can be obtained again by speaking to Yanni Salika for 100gp.

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
9 May 2013
(update | poll)

Yanni Salika will now sell you another bone key after completing Shilo Village so that you can revisit Rashiliyia's tomb. The key can now be added to the keyring.
